Â· Detection only
Â· Human intervention required
Â· Price: $X per instrument/month

Tier 2: Recipe-Based Correction (Phase 1 - 3 months)

Â· Deterministic fixes for common errors
Â· 80% of errors auto-corrected
Â· Price: $X + $Y per successful correction
Â· Value: Predictable MTTR, reduced technician time

Tier 3: Adaptive Correction (Phase 3 - 12+ months)

Â· RL-enhanced parameter optimization
Â· Novel error handling
Â· Price: Premium + % of savings
Â· Value: Continuous improvement, reduced protocol updates

