5.2 Risk Mitigation Strategy

Risk Likelihood Impact Mitigation
Recipe fails in novel scenario Medium High Tiered escalation + human oversight
False positive correction Low Medium Multi-modal verification
Instrument compatibility High Medium Standardized API + manufacturer partnerships
RL instability High High Shadow mode first + deterministic fallback

